---
title: Spicy Sweet Chorizo Pizza with Paprika Mayo and Salad
description: Taking a 'deluxe'-style pizza and making it TRULY deluxe, may we present to you our Spicy Sweet Chorizo Pizza! Topped with chorizo and our national treasure, maple syrup, this pizza shows you how big an impact simple ingredient swaps can have!
